content: Just implemented a new user training module for AI diagnostics. It's designed to help therapists understand the system better. Meanwhile, our blockchain team is refining the scalability protocols. Had a tech-free evening discussing the ethics of our work.

AI diagnostics now include predictive models for therapy resistance. We're seeing positive results in early trials. Also, our blockchain team is exploring new applications for our quantum-resistant system. Had a heart-to-heart with my partner about our career paths and the impact we want to make.
